verbose_text: 74 Although Catts et al. 75 found no changes in GFAP mRNA expression in the dorsolateral prefrontal cortex between schizophrenic patients and healthy controls, a difference was observed in schizophrenia patients when they were stratified based on the presence of other neuroinflammatory markers including serpin peptidase inhibitor (SERPIN) A3, IL-1beta, IL-6 and IL-8.
